data.title: Hongkongers Campaign to Oust China-Backed Leader
data.meta_description: Hong Kong is readying another test of China’s willingness to satisfy its democratic yearnings: a cross-party campaign to replace the city’s Beijing-backed but unpopular chief executive, Leung Chun-ying.
data.text:
Pro-business legislature candidates urge ‘Anyone But CY Leung’

No indication Chinese officials will withdraw crucial support

Hong Kong is readying another test of China’s willingness to satisfy its democratic yearnings: a cross-party campaign to replace the city’s Beijing-backed but unpopular chief executive, Leung Chun-ying .
